Christmas With Norman Rockwell
Gallery Books | 1990 | ISBN: 0831774223 | English | 88 pages | PDF | 15 MB

Capturing the warmth and nostalgia of the season, more than seventy-five paintings from the beloved American artist include family favorites spanning sixty years of Rockwell's career, along with commentary on the artist's life in a colorful keepsake volume
